  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Fri, 01/03/2014 - 12:19 | <a href="/news/2014-01-03/sign-top-hedge-fund-hiring-junior-bitcoin-execution-trader#comment-4296676" class="active">4296676</a></span>
