  <a href="/users/tip-e-canoe" title="View user profile."><img src="http://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/pictures/picture-7929.jpg" alt="tip e. canoe&#039;s picture" title="tip e. canoe&#039;s picture"  /></a></div>
