<div class="non_toggle_area" id="comment-4297399">
  <div class="non_toggle_label">
       <span class="scomments_info">Fri, 01/03/2014 - 15:34 | <a href="/news/2014-01-03/sign-top-hedge-fund-hiring-junior-bitcoin-execution-trader#comment-4297399" class="active">4297399</a></span>
              <b><a href="/users/sufiy" title="View user profile.">Sufiy</a></b>
  </div>

  <div class="comment-content">
    <div class="author"><div class="picture">
  <a href="/users/sufiy" title="View user profile."><img src="http://www.zerohedge.com/sites/default/files/pictures/picture-56548.jpg" alt="Sufiy&#039;s picture" title="Sufiy&#039;s picture"  /></a></div>
</div><div class="author"></div>
    <p><span><br />

<p>After The Crash: The Future of Bitcoin and Math Based Digital Currencies</p>

<p></p></span><span><br />
&nbsp; The video in the beginning of this discussion is the great explanation of the Bitcoin. And history of Crypto-currencies development is nothing less than fascinating. But there is the progress and there is an idea&nbsp;to get rich overnight. These are too very different things.&nbsp;
&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong><a href="http://sufiy.blogspot.co.uk/2013/12/european-banking-authority-warns.html#" rel="nofollow">We have the feeling that this entry will be at the right timing again</a>.</strong>&nbsp;There is always another crash coming to Bitcoin. It is not the question of the technological advance presented by Bitcoin, but it is the nature of its created Bubble.&nbsp;
&nbsp; After our last entry Bitcoin has recovered from low of 2011 to the 4742 at BTCChina. Now another shake out could be coming - the volume is going down dramatically as Bitcoin price is moving up. By the end of January China's ban on currency withdrawal will be in place. You can make your call when the next wave of selling will begin. It is quite interesting that Gold price is moving strongly up last few days with the new money being allocated to Gold.&nbsp;<a href="http://sufiy.blogspot.co.uk/2014/01/albert-cheng-gold-markets-move-east.html#" rel="nofollow"><strong>China encourages its citizens to accumulate gold and bans Bitcoin for its financial institutions.</strong></a>&nbsp;Will 2014 become the year of Great Rotation from Bubbles and into the real assets?


<a href="http://sufiy.blogspot.co.uk/2014/01/after-crash-future-of-bitcoin-and-math.html#" title="http://sufiy.blogspot.co.uk/2014/01/after-crash-future-of-bitcoin-and-math.html#">http://sufiy.blogspot.co.uk/2014/01/after-crash-future-of-bitcoin-and-ma...</a>
<p></p></span></p>

